<p><?php _e( 'The store may also accept credit cards for the payment. In order to accept credit card payments, the store complies with the industry security standards established by the major credit card companies (American Express, Discover, JCB, MasterCard, and Visa) to protect the buyers from cardholder information theft. Your details are safe with us as we take security very seriously.', 'dav2' ); ?></p>
